### Trigger Budget Analyst agent
POST http://localhost:8004/agent/run
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "task": "Calculate the budget for a corporate event with venue, catering, and entertainment"
}

### Trigger crash-test workflow
POST http://localhost:8001/run
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "prompt": "Calculate a budget for a corporate retreat with venue, catering, and entertainment"
}
